<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 16:07:49 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>受伤的以色列人质在加沙被哈马斯扣押的视频引发人们对其生命的严重担忧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article/.premium/video-of-wounded-israeli-hostage-held-by-hamas-in-gaza-raises-grave-concerns-for-his-life/0000018d-26fe-db77-ad9f-fffe49d30000</link><description>尼尔奥兹基布兹居民奥哈德·亚哈洛米 (Ohad Yahalomi) 于 10 月 7 日被哈马斯枪杀并带入加沙。他 12 岁的儿子 Eitan 也被扣为人质，并在被囚禁 52 天后于 11 月获释</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 14:03:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article/.premium/video-of-wounded-israeli-hostage-held-by-hamas-in-gaza-raises-grave-concerns-for-his-life/0000018d-26fe-db77-ad9f-fffe49d30000</guid></item><item><title>据称以色列袭击在大马士革造成至少四名伊朗革命卫队成员死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-01-20/ty-article/alleged-israeli-strike-kills-iranian-revolutionary-guards-members-in-damascus/0000018d-26bf-dd75-addd-f6ff9b2f0000</link><description>据消息人士称，这次袭击的目标是一座建筑，该建筑是支持巴沙尔·阿萨德总统政府的伊朗顾问使用的。死者中有叙利亚圣城军远征军情报负责人</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 12:33:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-01-20/ty-article/alleged-israeli-strike-kills-iranian-revolutionary-guards-members-in-damascus/0000018d-26bf-dd75-addd-f6ff9b2f0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登表示内塔尼亚胡并不反对针对巴勒斯坦人的所有两国解决方案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article/.premium/biden-says-netanyahu-not-opposed-to-all-two-state-solutions-for-palestinians/0000018d-25c9-daf5-a1bf-a5d92a5c0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 07:46:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article/.premium/biden-says-netanyahu-not-opposed-to-all-two-state-solutions-for-palestinians/0000018d-25c9-daf5-a1bf-a5d92a5c0000</guid></item><item><title>报告：四名以色列将军预测加沙旷日持久的战争可能会导致人质丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article-live/dozens-protest-outside-netanyahus-house-for-release-of-israeli-hostages-in-gaza/0000018d-24bd-db77-ad9f-ffbfec830000</link><description>革命卫队高级官员在大马士革的以色列袭击中丧生 ■ 海法反战抗议者示威 ■ 黎巴嫩报道：以色列无人机袭击提尔的汽车，造成两人死亡 ■ 数十名人质的家人在内塔尼亚胡家前抗议凯撒利亚 ■《纽约时报》报道，四名以色列国防军高级官员告诉他们，加沙的长期战争可能会导致人质丧生，以色列国防军发言人否认这一说法</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 03:52:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article-live/dozens-protest-outside-netanyahus-house-for-release-of-israeli-hostages-in-gaza/0000018d-24bd-db77-ad9f-ffbfec830000</guid></item><item><title>一枚以色列导弹，七名巴勒斯坦人死亡，其中四人是兄弟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-01-20/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/one-israeli-missile-seven-palestinians-killed-four-of-them-brothers/0000018d-2493-dd75-addd-f6f30b320000</link><description>一架以色列飞机在杰宁炸死了七名巴勒斯坦年轻人，其中一名巴勒斯坦人显然向一辆以色列军用吉普车投掷了爆炸装置，但没有击中。这七个人都来自同一个大家庭和同一个村庄</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 02:30:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-01-20/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/one-israeli-missile-seven-palestinians-killed-four-of-them-brothers/0000018d-2493-dd75-addd-f6f30b320000</guid></item><item><title>抗议者聚集在内塔尼亚胡家外呼吁释放以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article/.premium/protesters-gather-outside-netanyahus-house-calling-for-release-of-israeli-hostages/0000018d-23b2-db77-ad9f-ffb26d6c0000</link><description>数十人聚集在凯撒利亚总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的私人官邸外。梅拉夫·斯维尔斯基（Merav Svirsky）表示，“战斗危及人质，如果有办法把他们救出来，而唯一的办法就是达成有代价的协议，那就付出代价。”梅拉夫·斯维尔斯基的兄弟伊泰上周宣布被哈马斯杀害。</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 02:11:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article/.premium/protesters-gather-outside-netanyahus-house-calling-for-release-of-israeli-hostages/0000018d-23b2-db77-ad9f-ffb26d6c0000</guid></item><item><title>心理学研究表明，为什么以色列人不想知道加沙到底发生了什么</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article/.highlight/why-israelis-dont-want-to-know-whats-happening-in-gaza-according-to-psychology-research/0000018d-2478-db77-ad9f-ff7a9ada0000</link><description>行为研究的荟萃分析对一个奇怪的现象提出了质疑：是什么让人们对真相视而不见——例如在加沙？</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 01:50:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article/.highlight/why-israelis-dont-want-to-know-whats-happening-in-gaza-according-to-psychology-research/0000018d-2478-db77-ad9f-ff7a9ada0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列正面临着来自内部和外部的生存威胁。有一个解决方案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/israel-is-facing-existential-threats-from-inside-and-out-theres-one-solution/0000018d-243a-db77-ad9f-ff3af1d20000</link><description>以色列需要一场能够更新国家与公民之间契约的社会民主运动</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 01:22:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/israel-is-facing-existential-threats-from-inside-and-out-theres-one-solution/0000018d-243a-db77-ad9f-ff3af1d20000</guid></item><item><title>为什么《以色列的天才》的作者仍然认为它是世界上最好的国家之一</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/why-the-authors-of-the-genius-of-israel-think-its-one-of-the-worlds-best-countries/0000018d-22c8-dd75-addd-f2e9edd60000</link><description>创造“初创国家”一词的两位作家丹·塞纳和索尔·辛格出版了一本新书，赞扬以色列社会的幸福、健康和乐观——他们认为这些品质增强了以色列在战后几个月的恢复力加沙爆发</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 00:13:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-20/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/why-the-authors-of-the-genius-of-israel-think-its-one-of-the-worlds-best-countries/0000018d-22c8-dd75-addd-f2e9edd60000</guid></item><item><title>数十名以色列学生抗议批评以色列国防军和加沙战争的老师复职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-19/ty-article/.premium/dozens-of-israeli-students-protest-reinstatement-of-teacher-who-criticized-idf-gaza-war/0000018d-232a-d022-ad9d-2b3ef1c20000</link><description>梅厄·巴鲁钦 (Meir Baruchin) 因发表批评以色列军队的言论而被市政府解雇，并称其“谴责以色列国防军士兵、谴责以色列国和支持恐怖主义行为”，随后劳工法庭恢复了他的职位，学生们向他咒骂并吐口水。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 21:04:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-19/ty-article/.premium/dozens-of-israeli-students-protest-reinstatement-of-teacher-who-criticized-idf-gaza-war/0000018d-232a-d022-ad9d-2b3ef1c20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人向西岸团体开枪后，巴勒斯坦裔美国青少年被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-19/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-american-teenager-shot-dead-by-israelis-in-west-bank/0000018d-22ea-db77-ad9f-fffa26d00000</link><description>据军方消息人士称，一名下班警察和一名平民向一群向以色列汽车投掷石块的巴勒斯坦人开枪，开枪射击了一名 17 岁的受害者。</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 18:42:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-19/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-american-teenager-shot-dead-by-israelis-in-west-bank/0000018d-22ea-db77-ad9f-fffa26d00000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨，与内塔尼亚胡决裂并争取提前选举</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/gantz-break-with-netanyahu-and-fight-for-an-early-election/0000018d-2242-dd75-addd-f2e3f82a0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 16:37:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/gantz-break-with-netanyahu-and-fight-for-an-early-election/0000018d-2242-dd75-addd-f2e3f82a0000</guid></item><item><title>“战略错误”：以色列部长称战时内阁阻止了对黎巴嫩的先发制人打击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-19/ty-article/strategic-error-israeli-minister-says-war-govt-prevented-preemptive-strike-in-lebanon/0000018d-2274-d022-ad9d-2a7410810000</link><description>战时内阁部长加迪·艾森科特在接受采访时表示，内阁阻止了对黎巴嫩的先发制人打击，这“本来可以实现[哈马斯领导人叶海亚]辛瓦尔的战略愿景”</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 16:22:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-19/ty-article/strategic-error-israeli-minister-says-war-govt-prevented-preemptive-strike-in-lebanon/0000018d-2274-d022-ad9d-2a7410810000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙战斗中受伤身亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-dies-of-wounds-sustained-in-gaza-fighting/0000018d-2206-db77-ad9f-ff369aa80000</link><description>周三，来自赫兹利亚的 20 岁奥里·格尔比 (Ori Gerby) 在加沙地带南部被火箭弹击中身亡</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 15:26:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-dies-of-wounds-sustained-in-gaza-fighting/0000018d-2206-db77-ad9f-ff369aa80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列内阁讨论通过第三国向巴勒斯坦权力机构转移税收的提议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-discusses-proposal-to-transfer-tax-revenue-to-pa-via-third-country/0000018d-20d9-d022-ad9d-2afd1f910000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡总理内阁成员没有对财政部长贝扎雷尔·斯莫特里奇提出的提案进行投票</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 09:29:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-discusses-proposal-to-transfer-tax-revenue-to-pa-via-third-country/0000018d-20d9-d022-ad9d-2afd1f910000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对人质药品处理的业余态度是内塔尼亚胡所有弊病的一个症状</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-amateurish-handling-of-the-hostages-medicine-is-a-symptom-of-netanyahus-ills/0000018d-1e8c-dd75-addd-feedd5de0000</link><description>每一天都清楚地表明，总理的优先事项没有改变：首先是政治生存，然后是其他一切。 艾森科特和甘茨不再对战争有任何影响力，那么为什么他们仍然留在联盟中？ ■ Gallant 的未来已然清晰</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 04:01:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-amateurish-handling-of-the-hostages-medicine-is-a-symptom-of-netanyahus-ills/0000018d-1e8c-dd75-addd-feedd5de0000</guid></item><item><title>随着以色列在加沙的攻势不断推进，内塔尼亚胡政府变得更加妄想</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-19/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-government-gets-more-delusional-as-israels-campaign-in-gaza-grinds-on/0000018d-1e3d-dd75-addd-fefd93760000</link><description>有明显迹象表明，以色列正陷入加沙泥潭，约旦河西岸正处于沸点，但内塔尼亚胡和他的部长们却浑然不觉 ■ 人质的沙漏即将耗尽，以色列是时候重新考虑其优先事项了</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 04:01:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-19/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-government-gets-more-delusional-as-israels-campaign-in-gaza-grinds-on/0000018d-1e3d-dd75-addd-fefd93760000</guid></item><item><title>数十人在内塔尼亚胡家外抗议，要求释放加沙的以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-19/ty-article-live/u-s-reaffirms-two-state-commitment-as-netanyahu-vows-to-block-palestinian-state/0000018d-1fb6-db77-ad9f-dfb663820000</link><description>白宫：拜登和内塔尼亚胡讨论了以色列减少加沙平民伤害的责任 ■ 俄罗斯称哈马斯代表团在该国，敦促其释放人质 ■ 瑞士检察官称以色列总统赫尔佐格受到刑事投诉 ■ 以色列国防军：北部城市海法的警报造成拦截来自黎巴嫩的目标</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 03:22:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-19/ty-article-live/u-s-reaffirms-two-state-commitment-as-netanyahu-vows-to-block-palestinian-state/0000018d-1fb6-db77-ad9f-dfb663820000</guid></item><item><title>“我的儿子在加沙的一次爆炸中幸存下来。从那时起我就一直这样微笑着</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-01-19/ty-article/.highlight/my-son-survived-a-blast-in-gaza-ive-been-smiling-like-this-since/0000018d-1f0a-dd75-addd-ffeb6ecd0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：在战争中，两个孩子在军队里是什么感觉？哈马斯袭击新星党的幸存者选择不生气</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 00:43:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-01-19/ty-article/.highlight/my-son-survived-a-blast-in-gaza-ive-been-smiling-like-this-since/0000018d-1f0a-dd75-addd-ffeb6ecd0000</guid></item><item><title>战后加沙需要采取新的做法，但内塔尼亚胡仍坚持旧的幻想</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/post-war-gaza-warrants-a-fresh-approach-but-netanyahu-is-holding-on-to-old-fantasies/0000018d-1eeb-dd75-addd-feeb65050000</link><description>七十多年来，以色列提出了各种治理加沙的想法——从当地部族统治到将居民驱逐到西奈半岛。但巴勒斯坦人的变化需要新的方法</description><pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 00:10:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/post-war-gaza-warrants-a-fresh-approach-but-netanyahu-is-holding-on-to-old-fantasies/0000018d-1eeb-dd75-addd-feeb65050000</guid></item></channel></rss>